        "Danger": [
            "We've been getting reports that outlaws have been taking advantage of the outage, so be careful.",
            "Proceed with caution as the sector will not have ECN until the connection is back online.",
            "Take precautions when you head over to the site. With the array down we can't be sure what or who might be lurking out there.",
